# mkdocs-include-markdown-plugin

Mkdocs Markdown includer plugin.

<!-- mdpo-disable -->

[![PyPI][pypi-version-badge-link]][pypi-link]
[![Tests][tests-image]][tests-link]
[![Coverage status][coverage-image]][coverage-link]

